  "title": "ISic000634. Dedication to Zeus and Tyche",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-text=\"Διὶ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Διὶ</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">καὶ</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Τύχηι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τύχηι\"><span data-text=\"Τύχηι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">Τύχη<span class=\"small\" title=\"small character: ι\">ι</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\"><span data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">Μαρκιανός</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-text=\"Διὶ\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΔΙΙ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΚΑΙ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Τύχηι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τύχηι\"><span data-text=\"Τύχηι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">ΤΥΧΗ<span class=\"small\" title=\"small character: ι\">Ι</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\"><span data-text=\"Μαρκιανός\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΜΑΡΚΙΑΝΟΣ</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000634_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_leftthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_leftthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_leftthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_rightthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_rightthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_rightthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_rightthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000634_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000634_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Markianos (dedicated this) to Zeus and Tyche</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Bernabo Brea suggested linking this dedication to <a href=\"http://data.perseus.org/citations/urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi005.perseus-lat1:2.4.119\" target=\"_blank\">Cic. Verr.4.119</a> and the quarter of Tyche</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1994.0757 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a>  </li><li> 44.0787 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 1951.0255a <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a>  </li><li> Bernabò Brea NSA 1947 202-203 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1994 839 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001826\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001826</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Carefully carved letters, with minimal use of serifs, most visible on tau and chi; the iota adscript at the end of line 2 is small and mid-line; omicron is rhomboid in form, the hastae of the mu are all angled.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Δ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Δ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Η-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Η type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type4</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-tyoe3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ tyoe3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ type3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Χ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Χ type3</a> </p> Line 1  45-55  Line 2  45  Line 3  40-45  Interlineation line 1 to 3  30  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
